WEBVTT

00:00:27.960 --> 00:00:30.280
They kept the older generation close 
in their joys, sorrows,

00:00:30.280 --> 00:00:33.280
in all aspects of their lives.

00:00:33.280 --> 00:00:35.960
Similarly, Samar Jodha 
looked closely through his lens

00:00:35.960 --> 00:00:38.960
at the lives of the aging communities 
in our country,

00:00:38.960 --> 00:00:43.360
and he discovered that 
there is such an interesting perspective

00:00:43.360 --> 00:00:46.360
to life that we can find there.

00:00:46.360 --> 00:00:51.640
TED Talks India welcomes artist
and photographer, Samar Jodha.

00:00:51.750 --> 00:00:57.060
(Applause)